Differences between two TV Series

The aim of this exercise is to provide basic informations about 2 TV Series and see the ratings of every single episode given by site users. The site is http://www.imdb.com/ which contain ratings/comments/basic info of every movie or TV Series. The HTML site was parsed using rvest package, which is mainly used for parsing sites that doesn’t have tabular form.

The first TV Series is Game of Thrones, which belengs to Adventure, Drama, Fantasy cathegory and the overall grade is 9.5.
